{"tid":292780,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英解密文件曝光 五毛風向將轉","createTime":"2017-06-21T15:42:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-27T08:15:13.000Z","uid":23707,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"369358d24cfe2ee2afce71cc923806fd5cda8c1c","tid":292780,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T15:42:00.000Z","msg":"五毛匪成日話英國都唔比香港有民主<br />\n但係解密文件記載五十年代起英國已經想推香港民主制度<br />\n但係共匪威脅出兵先搞唔成<br />\n<br />\n所以五毛狗無得再講呢句垃圾言論<br />\n而改口話英國係四十年代之前都無搞民主<br />\n中共建國先搞 係因為想同中共對抗<br />\n唔係真係為香港好"},{"pid":"158626bc3a787de0d4ec7aa13dd9c039e9df2d05","tid":292780,"uid":49392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T16:00:30.000Z","msg":"戰後楊幕琦做翻港督後，曾經提出逐步建立議會民主，但當時商界擔心中國赤化後局勢，華人社會掛住搵食唔理"},{"pid":"87dc54df0ba3b16e17a11fdc9d270584d2305506","tid":292780,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T16:02:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69f93dfa064e0d9206b2f27ef552142f01c4ba2c","tid":292780,"uid":42764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T16:35:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e16895e76aa2685e86cad9502fe9c08fb45335a3","tid":292780,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T16:36:57.000Z","msg":"龍門任搬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9580854dcbfff4a23421cfecc9f5ee97ebc17b3","tid":292780,"uid":57705,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T16:40:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1b23cc12b642fea789d1f497cf07fec39e9ca1e1","tid":292780,"uid":116198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T16:44:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>戰後楊幕琦做翻港督後，曾經提出逐步建立議會民主，但當時商界擔心中國赤化後局勢，華人社會掛住搵食唔理</blockquote><br />\n其實早於19世紀已經有一班華人精英向港英爭取政治權力<br />\n先有D咩太平紳士，非官守議員等</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n劉皇發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dfb37d0aa27f1912625c6dbd1e715f9b048eefc","tid":292780,"uid":116198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T16:45:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>戰後楊幕琦做翻港督後，曾經提出逐步建立議會民主，但當時商界擔心中國赤化後局勢，華人社會掛住搵食唔理</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而家為咗搵食賣緊港添"},{"pid":"e7362785310aac73811004dfe0ed0abbb551ebb0","tid":292780,"uid":37030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T22:45:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4fc95bcfa6ebde4429f70625540bacd5c8559162","tid":292780,"uid":37030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T22:56:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b76a015ef078486fec158010ef99ee428e8e08c1","tid":292780,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T22:58:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>戰後楊幕琦做翻港督後，曾經提出逐步建立議會民主，但當時商界擔心中國赤化後局勢，華人社會掛住搵食唔理</blockquote><br />\n其實早於19世紀已經有一班華人精英向港英爭取政治權力<br />\n先有D咩太平紳士，非官守議員等</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n劉皇發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n未有解密文件<br />\n當唔知先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b48d914afb41a6054832b63fa38134e2ff933886","tid":292780,"uid":42764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T10:07:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b971a5c2d24c5e2348f4a81a684abb8fedce862","tid":292780,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T11:54:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e81fb64da461a17e1c51bf3702806f9771c25400","tid":292780,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T01:42:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18930837950a83277bed2957a4d5142cb17a44cc","tid":292780,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T02:57:03.000Z","msg":"話唔關支那事都冇人信啦<br />\n英國殖民地得香港要交畀第三世界國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f574b853feb4688bfa8085222b366bc05bb5238a","tid":292780,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T03:01:31.000Z","msg":"一路都公開係周恩來施壓<br />\n支那狗習慣選擇性失明je"},{"pid":"6ba31a0519acf15dfd6ea6ecb5f252d5a20b5143","tid":292780,"uid":41245,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T03:52:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一路都公開係周恩來施壓<br />\n支那狗習慣選擇性失明je</blockquote><br />\n佢地唔係失明<br />\n係要散播轉移視線要香港人唔好理英國人做嘅嘢啫<br />\n之前都爆過話英文有人肯幫香港去告英國政府，但前題要香港多人關注同畀證據<br />\n最後五毛最叻嘅手法就係散播話英國佬唔理，之後啲港豬又助攻一齊鬧英國<br />\n之前大把人講過，你會晒時間share啲大中華膠去見李飛，但唔肯去share（唔洗你自動去搞，只係㩒個like）係英國幫緊香港去向英國政府反映嘅人嘅呼籲"},{"pid":"88263bd2614498121296b071ae5c995f9a9d3c8a","tid":292780,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T15:11:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"880a0cc418da5e9525e9810c07cf78c871b58d68","tid":292780,"uid":44105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T15:34:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e63ea07b2bc5c2ff66fea732398a0c6aaf8b3d3d","tid":292780,"uid":65979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T15:45:03.000Z","msg":"不嬲都知有楊慕琦計劃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5d03cb69c7acfa5eb56b60f314d5ac258b93d64","tid":292780,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T15:52:31.000Z","msg":"爆料咪<br />\n周恩來 呢件狗雜種  向港英施壓<br />\n<br />\n不過條友都抵死  比毛狗當condom來用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3bd1197ca3f5b384f5762665de6086071ce28dd","tid":292780,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T15:54:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>爆料咪<br />\n周恩來 呢件狗雜種  向港英施壓<br />\n<br />\n不過條友都抵死  比毛狗當condom來用<img src=